<p>Is Darkblade the fourth blade because April is the fourth month, or am I reading too much into it?'</p>
<p>Also, am I wrong to think you intended the Wonder-Maker to be a prototypical Dr. Wondertainment? Is the Nothing-in-All a reference to the deleted All in Nothing, or whatever the sphere that likes worship was called? I get some of the other references (King-in-Scarlet, Mother of Them All, the Hanged King), but am a bit lost on some of the others. Would you be willing to elucidate?</p>

