			<div class="content" id="post-content-1770719">
									

<p>You're reading too far into that one.</p>
<p>Wonder-Maker is Wondertainment in an older, trickster-god form. The Nothing-In-All is 055. The Eternal Texts are 582. Carthac, Molug, and Gothog can be whoever you want them to be, really, though the first of those is based somewhat off of a acip in the tale <a href="/guard-duty">Guard Duty</a>. I was struggling for things to fill slots, you see.</p>

